{
  "text": "What was the catalyst for their change? I and Cora. In our peoples, there was what may be considered from the viewpoint of wisdom and overabundance of love. These entities looked at those still in darkness and saw that those of a neutral or somewhat negative a viewpoint profound such harmony, shall we say, sickening? The wanderers felt that a more wisdom oriented way of seeking love could be more appealing to those in a darkness. First, the one entity began its work. Quickly the second found the first. These entities had agreed to serve together, and so they did, glorifying the one creator, but not as they intended. About them were soon gathered those who found it easy to believe that a series of specific knowledges and wisdoms would advance one towards the Creator. The end of this was the graduation into fourth density, a negative of the wandererse, which had much power of personality, and some small deepening of the negatively polarized element of those not a polarizing positively.",
